  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Termo Rubiales</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IFC is investing in Termo Rubiales to support the development of Meta Petroleum, a promising player of the oil industry in Colombia that has embarked in an ambitious plan to increase the production of the Rubiales field. The investment in Termo Rubiales would be directly supportive of Government policies to increase local production and private investment in the oil sector.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project consists of the construction of a crude-oil fired thermal plant with gross capacity greater than 57 MW (Termo Rubiales or the Project), to supply energy to the Rubiales oil field (Rubiales) located in Los Llanos Orientales in Eastern Colombia.</narrative>
  </description>
